I spent my birthday this year stargazing. It’s been a rocky road for me the last several months. I have experienced grief, pain, sorrow, and more. All of which have required self-reflection and introspection. Sometimes you need a reset to reflect on how far you’ve traveled on your journey. It’s not always pretty, but I am grateful for growth, and the amazing support from so many incredible people in my life. When you come out the other side, open your eyes, and you will see that the sacrifices, as painful and difficult as they are, were all a necessary part of your journey. 🌙🪐✨
